            "stanza_text": "Là-bas, sous les arbres s'abrite\nUne chaumière au dos bossu ;\nLe toit penche, le mur s'effrite,\nLe seuil de la porte est moussu."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "La fenêtre, un volet la bouche ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Mais du taudis, comme au temps froid",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "La tiède haleine d'une bouche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "La respiration se voit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La fenêtre, un volet la bouche ;\nMais du taudis, comme au temps froid\nLa tiède haleine d'une bouche,\nLa respiration se voit."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Un tire-bouchon de fumée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Tournant son mince filet bleu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "De l'âme en ce bouge enfermée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Porte des nouvelles à Dieu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Un tire-bouchon de fumée,\nTournant son mince filet bleu,\nDe l'âme en ce bouge enfermée\nPorte des nouvelles à Dieu."
        }
